{"article_id":"YjkhFDAZscCyEEt7","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Sessions calls suggestion","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"he colluded with Russia","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"a 'detestable lie '","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"The attorney general also refused to answer questions about his conversations with Trump .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Attorney General Jeff Sessions forcefully defended his integrity on Tuesday ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"testifying","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"that any suggestion","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"he colluded with Russian officials","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"to affect the 2016 election","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"was \" a detestable lie , \"","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"even as he repeatedly refused to answer questions about his conversations with President Donald Trump .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"Sessions provided several fresh insights into his role in the Russia controversy","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"engulfing the Trump administration ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"revealing","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"that he has avoided internal Department of Justice conversations about the FBI ' s Russia probe","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"since he was sworn in ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"that he ' s never been briefed on Russia ' s alleged campaign","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"to affect the U.S. presidential race ,","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"and that he never warned FBI Director James Comey","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"that his job was on the line","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"before he was abruptly fired by Trump last month .","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"The attorney general , former Alabama senator and former Trump campaign adviser , also insisted","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"he did not recall having a third undisclosed meeting with Russian Ambassador Sergey Kislyak ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"as multiple reports","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"citing information","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"gathered by U.S. intelligence","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"have alleged .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"But Sessions ' testimony was far from an exoneration of the president ' s conduct ,","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"as the attorney general confirmed","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"that Comey had voiced concerns to him","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"that the president had initiated improper one-on-one contacts .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"Some of the hearing ' s most memorable moments came","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"as Sessions repeatedly","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"- and at times emotionally -","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"lashed out at allegations","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"that he and other Trump campaign advisers might have worked with Russian leaders","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"to try to tip the election Trump ' s way .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"\" The suggestion","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"that I participated in any collusion","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"or that I was aware of any collusion with the Russian government","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"to hurt this country ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"which I have served with honor for over 35 years ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"or to undermine the integrity of our democratic process , is an appalling and detestable lie , \"","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Sessions told the Senate Intelligence Committee .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"Sessions also pushed back against the idea","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"that he had more meetings with Kislyak ,","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"after having been forced to clarify remarks from his confirmation hearing in January","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"that he did not have communications with Russian officials during the campaign .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Two previous meetings with Kisylak surfaced earlier this year ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"but Sessions said on Tuesday","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"he doesn ' t remember any further encounters ,","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"including an allegation","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"he met with Kislyak in April 2016 at the Mayflower Hotel in Washington ,","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"which hosted a foreign policy speech by Trump .","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"\" I did not have any private meetings","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"nor do I recall any conversations with any Russian officials at the Mayflower Hotel , \"","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"Sessions said .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"He later elaborated","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"that a brief interaction with Kislyak may have occurred ,","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"noting","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"that \" I may have had an encounter during the reception \"","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"but that would have been the extent of any communication .","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"Sessions took his uncomfortable star turn in the same seat","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"occupied by Comey five days before","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"as the former FBI director pointedly accused Trump of lying about his dismissal .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Sessions has found himself at the center of the Russian controversy in recent days ,","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"particularly after Comey testified","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"that he had asked Sessions to intervene","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"after Trump initiated a series of contacts about the Russia probe","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"that the FBI director viewed as improper .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"Comey also suggested","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"Sessions realized something inappropriate was afoot","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"when Trump asked Comey to stay behind at an Oval Office meeting in February ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"while dismissing Sessions and others from the room .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"\" My sense was the attorney general knew","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"he shouldn ' t be leaving ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"which is why he was lingering , \"","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"Comey testified .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"Playbook newsletter","depth":4},{"id":79,"text":"Sign up today","depth":5},{"id":80,"text":"to receive the # 1-rated newsletter in politics","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"Email Sign Up","depth":4},{"id":82,"text":"By signing up","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"you agree to receive email newsletters or alerts from .","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"You can unsubscribe at any time .","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"and the Google Privacy Policy and Terms of Service apply .","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"Comey also said","depth":5},{"id":88,"text":"that in the one-on-one meeting","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"that followed ,","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"Trump asked","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"that the FBI \" let ... go \" of a probe into former national security adviser Michael Flynn .","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"Trump has said","depth":5},{"id":93,"text":"he made no such request .","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"Sessions denied on Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"that he stayed silent","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"when Comey urged him never to leave him alone again with Trump .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"The attorney general testified","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"that he urged the FBI and DOJ officials to follow proper protocol in their communications with the White House .","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"That directly contradicts Comey ' s testimony on Thursday ,","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"when the ex-FBI chief said","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"Sessions had no verbal response","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"when Comey told the attorney general","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"that being left alone with Trump was inappropriate","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"and should not happen .","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"A DOJ spokesman rejected Comey ' s account","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"following last week ' s hearing .","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"\" He didn ' t recall this ,","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"but I responded to his comment","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"by agreeing","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"that the FBI and the Department of Justice needed to be careful to follow department policies regarding appropriate contacts with the White House , \"","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"Sessions testified .","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"However , Sessions did not say","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"whether he made any effort","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"to stop Trump from contacting the FBI ,","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"such as intervening with the president directly or seeking to pass such a message through the White House counsel or other officials .","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"The attorney general ' s closely watched testimony came","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"as Washington buzzed about suggestions from Trump allies","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"that the president was considering firing the man","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"tapped last month","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"to take over the probe into alleged Russian interference in the 2016 election :","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"special counsel Robert Mueller .","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"Sessions would not specifically talk about Mueller ' s job performance ,","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"but said ,","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"\" I have confidence in Mr. Mueller . \"","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"The attorney general cited his recusal from the Russia probe as one of the reasons","depth":6},{"id":126,"text":"he could not elaborate on Mueller .","depth":6},{"id":127,"text":"In March , Sessions declared","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"because of his role in the Trump campaign","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"he was recusing himself from all inquiries","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"related to Russia ' s alleged interference in the 2016 elections .","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"During his testimony on Tuesday , Sessions disclosed more details of the timeline of his recusal :","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"One day after he was sworn in as attorney general on Feb. 9 ,","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"Sessions had his first meeting","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"to generally discuss the recusal matter .","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"Several meetings followed ,","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"and \" it became clear to me over time","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"that I qualified as a significant principal adviser type person to the campaign","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"and it would be appropriate and the right thing for me to recuse myself . \"","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"His recusal from matters","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"related to the presidential campaign ,","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"which","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"Sessions said","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"was essentially in place from his first day as attorney general ,","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"is apparently so broad","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"that he has never been briefed on Russian hacking attempts last year .","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"\" I never received any detailed briefing","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"on how the hacking occurred , \"","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"Sessions testified ,","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"he had gotten his information about Russian interference in the 2016 campaign only through the news media .","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"Speaking to Sen. Angus King","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"( I-Maine ) ,","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"Sessions added","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"that \" you might have been very critical","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"if I , as an active part of the campaign , was seeking intelligence","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"related to something","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"that might be relevant to the campaign . \"","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"Sessions also said Tuesday","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"that he would not claim executive privilege","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"as he testified","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"\" because that is the president ' s power. \"","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"But he added","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"that he would abide by long-standing DOJ practice","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"to shield his discussions with Trump .","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"\" I can not and will not violate my duty","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"to protect confidential communications with the president , \"","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"Sessions refused to answer a pivotal question from Sen. Dianne Feinstein","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"( D-Calif. ) :","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"Whether he discussed Comey ' s handling of the investigations into the Trump campaign with the president prior to the FBI director ' s dismissal .","depth":8},{"id":172,"text":"\" I ' m not able to discuss with you","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"or confirm or deny the nature of a private conversation","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"that I may have had with the president on this subject or others .","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"I know","depth":12},{"id":176,"text":"this will be discussed ,","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"but that ' s the rules","depth":12},{"id":178,"text":"that have been adhered to by the Department of Justice , \"","depth":12},{"id":179,"text":"Sessions said .","depth":8},{"id":180,"text":"Asked to react to Trump ' s public statement","depth":9},{"id":181,"text":"that he had the Russia probe on his mind at the time of the firing ,","depth":9},{"id":182,"text":"the attorney general demurred .","depth":8},{"id":183,"text":"\" I will have to let his words speak for himself .","depth":8},{"id":184,"text":"I ' m not sure","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"what was in his mind specifically","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"when we talked to him , \"","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"Sessions said .","depth":9},{"id":188,"text":"As Sessions declined to answer a series of questions ,","depth":6},{"id":189,"text":"Democrats bluntly accused him of undermining Congress ' effort","depth":7},{"id":190,"text":"to get to the truth .","depth":7},{"id":191,"text":"Sen. Ron Wyden of Oregon said","depth":8},{"id":192,"text":"the lack of responses amounted to stonewalling .","depth":8},{"id":193,"text":"\" I am not stonewalling .","depth":9},{"id":194,"text":"I am following the historic policies of the Department of Justice , \"","depth":9},{"id":195,"text":"the attorney general declared .","depth":8},{"id":196,"text":"\" You ' re impeding this investigation , \"","depth":8},{"id":197,"text":"Sen. Martin Heinrich of New Mexico said .","depth":8},{"id":198,"text":"\" You are obstructing that congressional investigation","depth":8},{"id":199,"text":"by not answering the questions . \"","depth":8},{"id":200,"text":"Resolving a long-standing question ,","depth":7},{"id":201,"text":"Sessions acknowledged publicly for the first time Tuesday","depth":8},{"id":202,"text":"that he gave Comey no warning before his firing on May 9 .","depth":8},{"id":203,"text":"\" Did you ever have a conversation about his failure","depth":10},{"id":204,"text":"to perform ? \"","depth":10},{"id":205,"text":"Sen. Mark Warner , the ranking Democrat on the committee , asked .","depth":9},{"id":206,"text":"\" You never thought","depth":10},{"id":207,"text":"it was appropriate to raise those concerns","depth":11},{"id":208,"text":"before he was actually terminated by the president ? \"","depth":11},{"id":209,"text":"Warner asked .","depth":9},{"id":210,"text":"\" I did not do so , \"","depth":10},{"id":211,"text":"Sessions said ,","depth":10},{"id":212,"text":"noting","depth":10},{"id":213,"text":"that Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein prepared a memo","depth":11},{"id":214,"text":"critiquing Comey ' s performance .","depth":11},{"id":215,"text":"\" It ' s something","depth":10},{"id":216,"text":"that we both agreed to","depth":10},{"id":217,"text":"that a fresh start at the FBI was probably the best . \"","depth":9},{"id":218,"text":"Democratic senators and Comey have suggested","depth":10},{"id":219,"text":"that Sessions should not have been involved in the firing of the FBI director ,","depth":10},{"id":220,"text":"particularly since investigations","depth":11},{"id":221,"text":"from which Sessions was recused","depth":11},{"id":222,"text":"appear to have played roles","depth":11},{"id":223,"text":"in spurring that decision .","depth":11},{"id":224,"text":"\" It is absurd , frankly , to suggest","depth":10},{"id":225,"text":"that a recusal from a single specific investigation would render an attorney general unable to manage the leadership of the various Department of Justice law enforcement components","depth":11},{"id":226,"text":"that conduct thousands of investigations , \"","depth":11},{"id":227,"text":"Sessions said .","depth":9},{"id":228,"text":"The usually genial Alabamian showed outbursts of anger ,","depth":9},{"id":229,"text":"including under questioning from Wyden ,","depth":10},{"id":230,"text":"who pressed Sessions on what Comey found so \" problematic \" about the attorney general","depth":11},{"id":231,"text":"that he felt","depth":12},{"id":232,"text":"his recusal was inevitable .","depth":12},{"id":233,"text":"\" Why don ' t you tell me ? \"","depth":10},{"id":234,"text":"Sessions responded ,","depth":11},{"id":235,"text":"his tone escalating .","depth":11},{"id":236,"text":"\" There are none ...","depth":10},{"id":237,"text":"this is a secret innuendo . \"","depth":10},{"id":238,"text":"Sessions also offered his firsthand account of the Feb. 14 Oval Office encounter","depth":9},{"id":239,"text":"that resulted in Comey being alone with Trump .","depth":9},{"id":240,"text":"\" We were there .","depth":10},{"id":241,"text":"I was standing there","depth":11},{"id":242,"text":"and","depth":13},{"id":243,"text":"without revealing any conversation","depth":16},{"id":244,"text":"that took place ,","depth":16},{"id":245,"text":"what I do recall is","depth":15},{"id":246,"text":"I did depart .","depth":14},{"id":247,"text":"I believe","depth":15},{"id":248,"text":"everyone else did depart","depth":15},{"id":249,"text":"and Director Comey was sitting in front of the president ' s desk","depth":15},{"id":250,"text":"and they were talking . ...","depth":15},{"id":251,"text":"That in itself is not problematic , \"","depth":13},{"id":252,"text":"Sessions said .","depth":9},{"id":253,"text":"The attorney general confirmed","depth":9},{"id":254,"text":"that the next day Comey complained about the contact .","depth":9},{"id":255,"text":"\" He did not tell me at that time any detail about anything","depth":11},{"id":256,"text":"that was said","depth":12},{"id":257,"text":"that was improper , \"","depth":12},{"id":258,"text":"Sessions said ,","depth":10},{"id":259,"text":"claiming","depth":11},{"id":260,"text":"he \" backed [ Comey ] up in his concern \" about improper contacts .","depth":11},{"id":261,"text":"\" He was concerned about it . ...","depth":11},{"id":262,"text":"His recollection of what he said about his concern is consistent with my recollection , \"","depth":12},{"id":263,"text":"the attorney general added .","depth":12}],"relations":[{"parent":527,"left":350,"right":526,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":350,"left":341,"right":349,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":341,"left":294,"right":340,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":294,"left":274,"right":293,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":267,"right":273,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":267,"left":266,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":265,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":265,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":272,"right":10,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":4,"right":271,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":5,"right":270,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":270,"left":269,"right":9,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":269,"left":6,"right":268,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":268,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":293,"left":289,"right":292,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":289,"left":283,"right":288,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":283,"left":275,"right":282,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":275,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":282,"left":13,"right":281,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":281,"left":276,"right":280,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":276,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":280,"left":277,"right":279,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":277,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":279,"left":278,"right":20,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":288,"left":284,"right":287,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":284,"left":21,"right":22,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":287,"left":286,"right":26,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":286,"left":23,"right":285,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":24,"right":25,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":292,"left":27,"right":291,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":291,"left":28,"right":290,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":290,"left":29,"right":30,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":340,"left":306,"right":339,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":306,"left":299,"right":305,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":299,"left":31,"right":298,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":298,"left":296,"right":297,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":296,"left":295,"right":34,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":295,"left":32,"right":33,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":297,"left":35,"right":36,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":305,"left":304,"right":43,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":304,"left":301,"right":303,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":301,"left":37,"right":300,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":38,"right":39,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":303,"left":302,"right":42,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":302,"left":40,"right":41,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":339,"left":331,"right":338,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":331,"left":323,"right":330,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":323,"left":309,"right":322,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":309,"left":307,"right":308,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":307,"left":44,"right":45,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":308,"left":46,"right":47,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":322,"left":314,"right":321,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":314,"left":48,"right":313,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":313,"left":310,"right":312,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":310,"left":49,"right":50,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":312,"left":51,"right":311,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":311,"left":52,"right":53,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":321,"left":316,"right":320,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":316,"left":315,"right":56,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":315,"left":54,"right":55,"relation":"joint","nucl